{"cced-ctron-joern-battle-over-sapphire": {"frequency": "REGULAR", "repeat": "ONCE", "condition": "party.alive.Glasses && party.alive.Joern && area.forest.isCurrent", "eventType": "PARALLEL", "runOnTrigger": [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6], "event": [{"type": "IF", "withElse": false, "condition": "call.runCount == 1", "thenStep": [{"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Can't find places like this back at home."}, "person": {"person": "antagonists.sidekick", "expression": "SMILE"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Sapphire Ridge... A mysterious forest, permanently shrouded in twilight."}, "person": {"person": "main.glasses", "expression": "DEFAULT"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Peaceful and relaxing, isn't it."}, "person": {"person": "antagonists.sidekick", "expression": "SMILE"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " [nods]"}, "person": {"person": "main.lea", "expression": "NOD"}}]}, {"type": "IF", "withElse": false, "condition": "call.runCount == 2", "thenStep": [{"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Did you know that perpetual dusk is a very rare planetary anomaly?"}, "person": {"person": "main.glasses", "expression": "DOWN"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " For that to be natural, Raritan Gem must have synchronous rotation with the star."}, "person": {"person": "main.glasses", "expression": "SURPRISED"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " But something isn't right...\\! The climate should be much more hostile."}, "person": {"person": "main.glasses", "expression": "WORRIED"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Relax and enjoy the atmosphere, Tronny."}, "person": {"person": "antagonists.sidekick", "expression": "SMILE"}}]}, {"type": "IF", "withElse": false, "condition": "call.runCount == 3", "thenStep": [{"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Almost entirety of this moon is water, yet we never see any storms or waves."}, "person": {"person": "main.glasses", "expression": "DOWN"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Large waves would be disastrous for beach areas."}, "person": {"person": "antagonists.sidekick", "expression": "DEFAULT"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " And to avoid waves, Raritan Gem must be tidally locked..."}, "person": {"person": "main.glasses", "expression": "WORRIED"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Sounds plausible."}, "person": {"person": "antagonists.sidekick", "expression": "DEFAULT"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " But then it may orbit behind gas giant, blocking the light..."}, "person": {"person": "main.glasses", "expression": "EXHAUSTED"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Unless..."}, "person": {"person": "main.glasses", "expression": "BLANK"}}]}, {"type": "IF", "withElse": false, "condition": "call.runCount == 4", "thenStep": [{"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Unless it doesn't \\c[3]rotate\\c[0] nor \\c[3]revolve\\c[0] around gas giant?"}, "person": {"person": "antagonists.sidekick", "expression": "DEFAULT"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " No, what a nonsense. That's impossibly rare."}, "person": {"person": "main.glasses", "expression": "EXHAUSTED"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " On top of that, perfectly habitable atmosphere and gravity?"}, "person": {"person": "main.glasses", "expression": "DOWN"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " The water and illumination are just not real."}, "person": {"person": "main.glasses", "expression": "WORRIED"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " ..."}, "person": {"person": "main.lea", "expression": "EXHAUSTED"}}]}, {"type": "IF", "withElse": false, "condition": "call.runCount == 5", "thenStep": [{"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " There are also hundreds of instanced rooms for every player..."}, "person": {"person": "main.glasses", "expression": "DEFAULT"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " No way they hollowed out the entire continent to built them. It's just too much terraforming."}, "person": {"person": "main.glasses", "expression": "WORRIED"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " That means only one thing..."}, "person": {"person": "main.glasses", "expression": "BLANK"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Tronny."}, "person": {"person": "antagonists.sidekick", "expression": "DEFAULT"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Not only water and light are fake!"}, "person": {"person": "main.glasses", "expression": "CRAZY_PANIC"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " \\c[1]The entire moon must be simulated!!\\c[0]"}, "person": {"person": "main.glasses", "expression": "CRAZY_PANIC2"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Relax, Tronny."}, "person": {"person": "antagonists.sidekick", "expression": "SARCASTIC"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Relax."}, "person": {"person": "antagonists.sidekick", "expression": "EX2_TRANQUIL"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " ..."}, "person": {"person": "main.lea", "expression": "SLEEPING"}}]}, {"type": "IF", "withElse": false, "condition": "call.runCount == 6", "thenStep": [{"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Okay, maybe that was a bit too crazy."}, "person": {"person": "main.glasses", "expression": "EXHAUSTED"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Raritan Gem is real. There are ships with maintenance crew after all."}, "person": {"person": "main.glasses", "expression": "THOUGHTFUL"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " But illumination... it's clearly artificial...\\. like every other special effect."}, "person": {"person": "main.glasses", "expression": "WORRIED"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " What if moon is also artificial?"}, "person": {"person": "antagonists.sidekick", "expression": "TOWARD"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Like, all metal on the inside?"}, "person": {"person": "antagonists.sidekick", "expression": "SARCASTIC"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Oh no..."}, "person": {"person": "main.glasses", "expression": "PANIC"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " ..."}, "person": {"person": "main.lea", "expression": "SMILE"}}, {"type": "CHANGE_VAR_NUMBER", "varName": "cced.ctron-joern.tourism.locations", "value": 1, "changeType": "add"}, {"type": "CHANGE_VAR_BOOL", "varName": "cced.ctron-joern.tourism.sapphire", "value": true, "changeType": "set"}]}], "overrideSideMessage": false, "loopCount": 3, "type": {"killCount": 0, "type": "BATTLE_OVER"}}}